title: Alemanio Fini
body: He wrote a work with the following title: Descritione dell Isola d'illa Madera written in the Latin language by Count Giulio Landi, Piacenza, 1574.

Alemanio Fini: Author of the work Descritione dell Isola d'illa Madera

1574: Publication of the work Descritione dell Isola d'illa Madera
